> > > > > > for VRR this targets the highest frame rate possible for the current
> > > > > > VRR mode, right?
> > > > > >
> > > > >
> > > > > It is based on vblank->framedur_ns which is in turn based on
> > > > > mode->crtc_clock.  Presumably for VRR that ends up being a maximum?
